# Webhook URL for daily push notification.
# Leave empty to skip notifications (digest still saved to digests/).
#
# Pick ONE channel and set WEBHOOK_URL to its full URL. The sender is
# auto-detected from the URL domain, so a single secret covers all of them.
#
# --- 企业微信群机器人 (WeChat Work group robot) ---
# Group settings -> Group bot -> Add bot, copy the webhook URL.
# https://qyapi.weixin.qq.com/cgi-bin/webhook/send?key=YOUR_KEY
#
# --- 钉钉自定义机器人 (DingTalk custom robot) ---
# Group settings -> Smart assistant -> Add bot -> Custom, copy the webhook URL.
# Safety: pick "custom keyword" and use "新闻".
# https://oapi.dingtalk.com/robot/send?access_token=YOUR_TOKEN
#
# --- Server酱 -> 个人微信 (ServerChan / personal WeChat) ---
# 微信扫码登录 https://sct.ftqq.com/ 拿到 SendKey，拼成下面的 URL。
# 消息通过 Server酱 小程序/公众号 推到你的微信。免费版每天 5 条，够用。
# https://sctapi.ftqq.com/YOUR_SENDKEY.send
#
# --- PushPlus -> 个人微信 (personal WeChat) ---
# 微信扫码登录 https://www.pushplus.plus/ 并关注公众号，拿到 token，拼成下面的 URL。
# https://www.pushplus.plus/send?token=YOUR_TOKEN
#
# In GitHub, set this as a repository secret named WEBHOOK_URL:
#   Settings -> Secrets and variables -> Actions -> New repository secret
WEBHOOK_URL=
